post_text:
After meeting with the local health departments and area superintendents concerning the corona virus crisis it has been decided that we will be canceling school starting tomorrow, Tuesday the 17th. All school activities, contests, practices and events here at Schuyler R-1 Schools will be canceled as well. The date to come back to school as of now is April 6th. There are to be no activities in the buildings during this time of shut down. This is obviously a difficult decision and unprecedented in our lifetime. This will cause hardship for many in the district and we certainly appreciate everyone for their patience, support, and understanding. We will do our best to communicate with all parties as we continue to monitor the situation.

Thank you
text:
After meeting with the local health departments and area superintendents concerning the corona virus crisis it has been decided that we will be canceling school starting tomorrow, Tuesday the 17th. All school activities, contests, practices and events here at Schuyler R-1 Schools will be canceled as well. The date to come back to school as of now is April 6th. There are to be no activities in the buildings during this time of shut down. This is obviously a difficult decision and unprecedented in our lifetime. This will cause hardship for many in the district and we certainly appreciate everyone for their patience, support, and understanding. We will do our best to communicate with all parties as we continue to monitor the situation.

Thank you
